thread.title: A Luxury Tower Rises Next to … Honk! … the Lincoln Tunnel

author: Josh Barbanel
title: A Luxury Tower Rises Next to … Honk! … the Lincoln Tunnel
text:
It is wider than the most famous Manhattan boulevards like Fifth Avenue or Central Park West.
But the location, next to 10 lanes of ramps leading to the Lincoln Tunnel, is somewhat less glamorous.
Yet a developer believes that with some good soundproofing he can bring luxury living to one of the bleakest stretches of New York real estate.
